NEW YORK CITY
Dong Kingman, the award winning Chinese-American artist, travels the world sketching and painting
the beautiful, the monumental and the picturesque. His watercolors grace more than forty
permanent museum and private collections in the USA and abroad.
One of the most remarkable real estate deals in history was negotiated in 1624 when Peter Minuit
bouaht the island of Manhattan from the Indians for a reported $24 worth of trinkets.
Today, a city of almost 8 million people, New York is perhaps the greatest port in the world and the
financial, intellectual and artistic center of the United States of America. If is a city of superlatives,
in a class by itself. Pan Am serves New York every day on its Round-the-World flights, and one
can reach New York on Pan Am from virtualiv anywhere in the word.
@PAN AM
